dataObject.content: CNN anchor Chris Cuomo was quick to defend climate activist Greta Thunberg from "Trumpers" who mocked her on Thursday but was quickly reminded about the settlement his network recently made with Covington Catholic High School student Nick Sandmann.

annotationData.content: {"category":{"label":"Unbiased"},"rationale":"There is nothing biased about defending somebody from attacks from people of different political beliefs."}

{"category":{"label":"Unbiased"},"rationale":"Although this news seems to come from a potentially conservative news outlet, I would not say it is biased because it is simply reporting on Cuomo, Turnberg, and Sandmann and not stating whether they like or dislike these individuals or their behavior."}
